---
title: Roast Pumpkin & Creamy Feta Lasagne with Rocket Salad
description: Comfort food just got a glow-up! This veggie-packed lasagne layers sweet, golden pumpkin with luscious feta and perfectly baked pasta sheets, all served with a peppery rocket salad for a fresh little kick. It’s cosy, cheesy, and anything but ordinary.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y25_R1037_W22_NZ_Main_6_high-f3ce1044.jpg
